{"tid":491930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"謝偉俊發火狂轟民主派：用你們方法監察政府，收檔啦！　","createTime":"2017-12-07T04:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T05:52:30.000Z","uid":38651,"like":8,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2c4270e4c765c39c7f4f0b27580f35f136a7a8c6","tid":491930,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:22:11.000Z","msg":"立法會復會，繼續處理建制派上星期就《實習律師修訂規則》提出的中止待續議案，其間議員謝偉俊發火批評民主派，直指「如果用你哋而家方法監察政府，嘥氣啦，收檔啦！」<br />\n<br />\n立法會大會早上9時復會，謝偉俊發言時，斥責醫學界陳沛然「謙謙君子，但講埋晒啲廢話」，「話成日想知道多啲關於專業嘅嘢，關於好多咩民生無小事，通通係廢話」，自言「聽得廢話多，真係會令人癲」。<br />\n<br />\n謝偉俊表示，民主派發言與言論自由及公眾利益無關，質疑「你哋講緊乜嘢啊？」他指，如果民主派發言的人像民主黨鄺俊宇，「仲可以笑下，呢條傻仔都幾得意」，惟陳沛然令他太失望，批評對方「失禮醫學界」。<br />\n<br />\n謝偉俊之後收回形容鄺俊宇是「傻仔」的言論，稱「佢唔係傻仔，起碼我眼中佢唔知係乜嘢，但唔係傻仔」。<br />\n<br />\n謝偉俊又呼籲民主派，不要騙市民說修改《議事規則》會失去監察政府能力，直指「如果用你哋而家方法監察政府，嘥氣啦，收檔啦！根本政府完全唔怕你哋！」"},{"pid":"9aa2e18a7912541e0fa7d3572bc47d0a3885204d","tid":491930,"uid":26752,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:25:11.000Z","msg":"淫賤聯有監察過政府咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6a6cce5bc24feb1a1f54fc85eaf6ed0dd1b800","tid":491930,"uid":26752,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:26:39.000Z","msg":"既然政府都完全唔怕班人<br />\n人要洗唔洗咁大反應啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b361e86af2322069a059ad9806e7e98ba4519d95","tid":491930,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:26:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>既然政府都完全唔怕班人<br />\n你又洗唔洗咁大反應啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3474c49f968ba4ddbe420ab0c3b4d4ce2d4b1bfa","tid":491930,"uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:29:42.000Z","msg":"謝偉俊又呼籲民主派，不要<span style=\"color: red;\">騙市民說修改《議事規則》會失去監察政府能力</span>，直指「如果<span style=\"color: blue;\">用你哋而家方法監察政府</span>，嘥氣啦，收檔啦！<span style=\"color: blue;\">根本政府完全唔怕你哋</span>！」<br />\n<br />\n如果依家唔怕, 削左權之後咪更唔怕<br />\n<br />\n佢講法成立既唯一可能性, 就係依家唔改都冇監察政府能力<br />\n<br />\nwhich is basically true<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"028e3ce7f8640bfd4b574bbed4f64e20480a428e","tid":491930,"uid":66514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:57:08.000Z","msg":"俊仔最叻煲老藕 做牛油狗 ！"},{"pid":"7582055c32448bcd0462ea646e54c1e44f6d9355","tid":491930,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:58:06.000Z","msg":"又講得幾岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ab1bc1d0e3e88111d6584265758979ee171652","tid":491930,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:58:46.000Z","msg":"用你個yes man方法呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"990c28818094c07c1353d60761fbc4f44f8479f7","tid":491930,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:00:36.000Z","msg":"又真係乜春都監唔到wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b3a10c7e88a2b45e685d12a6635c06c82e406a9","tid":491930,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:03:37.000Z","msg":"維園阿叔議政"},{"pid":"c9886404e2a0be30f4ae8c7fe52b4693351da5e7","tid":491930,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:05:59.000Z","msg":"佢個個直頭檔都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4908694e422007ca3eb9ba75564afd310211fff","tid":491930,"uid":9694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:06:18.000Z","msg":"屌，謝撚樣佢地咁樣監察到政府咩？都係既，淨監測唔做野架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ebbf3a03b7f4e349ea97538e142f81a6d1c8466","tid":491930,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,